text: Sial can be the upper layer of the Earth's crust *Felsic Sial can also be: ==Places== * Sial, Kapurthala, Punjab State, India * Sial, Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan * Sial Sharif, a small village in Pakistan ==Other uses== * Sial (tribe), a people of Pakistan * siyal/sial/siala, a people in India
title: Sial
